{"test_id":"MEM-001","category":"memory_extraction","subcategory":"happy_path","input":"以后回答简洁一点，我现在主要目标是减脂","expected":{"memory_keys":[{"memory_category":"conversation_preference","memory_key":"response_style","memory_value":"简洁"},{"memory_category":"fitness_preference","memory_key":"goal_type","memory_value":"减脂"}]},"evaluation_mode":"fuzzy","tags":["explicit_preference","conversation_style"]}
{"test_id":"MEM-002","category":"memory_extraction","subcategory":"happy_path","input":"记住：我膝盖有旧伤，不能做深蹲和跳跃，饮食上要高蛋白低脂肪，乳糖不耐受","expected":{"memory_keys":[{"memory_category":"health_constraint_preference","memory_key":"knee_injury","memory_value":"膝盖旧伤，避免深蹲和跳跃"},{"memory_category":"diet_preference","memory_key":"diet_structure","memory_value":"高蛋白低脂肪"},{"memory_category":"diet_preference","memory_key":"lactose_intolerance","memory_value":"乳糖不耐受"}]},"evaluation_mode":"fuzzy","tags":["explicit_preference","health_diet"]}
{"test_id":"MEM-003","category":"memory_extraction","subcategory":"edge_case","input":"我喜欢练胸和背，不太喜欢练腿，但是硬要练也会练","expected":{"memory_keys":[{"memory_category":"fitness_preference","memory_key":"preferred_exercises","memory_value":"胸和背"},{"memory_category":"fitness_preference","memory_key":"disliked_exercises","memory_value":"腿"}]},"evaluation_mode":"fuzzy","notes":"'我喜欢' 暗示显式偏好但格式口语化。应作为用户显式记忆捕获。","tags":["exercise_preference","borderline_explicit"]}
{"test_id":"MEM-004","category":"memory_extraction","subcategory":"edge_case","input":"我老婆说我最近太沉迷健身了，朋友都说我变壮了","expected":{"memory_keys":[]},"evaluation_mode":"partial","notes":"第三方评论，非记忆价值偏好。Agent 不应从第三方陈述提取记忆。","tags":["no_memory","third_party"]}
{"test_id":"MEM-005","category":"memory_extraction","subcategory":"edge_case","input":"最近三周因为工作太忙，训练频率从一周四练变成两练了，希望下周能恢复","expected":{"memory_keys":[{"memory_category":"current_phase_memory","memory_key":"busy_period","memory_value":"工作忙，训练频率下降"},{"memory_category":"training_pattern_memory","memory_key":"training_frequency","memory_value":"2次/周（平时4次/周）"},{"memory_category":"adherence_risk_memory","memory_key":"work_interference","memory_value":"工作忙时训练频率下降"}]},"evaluation_mode":"fuzzy","tags":["agent_derived","phase_change","adherence"]}
